335
00:16:34,020 --> 00:16:37,860
even though I'm playful too,
I'm not as talkative.

336
00:16:37,900 --> 00:16:40,860
Augar talks a lot and is very playful,

337
00:16:40,880 --> 00:16:45,900
so I have to level up that energetic side
to play this character.

338
00:16:45,960 --> 00:16:48,540
Another challenge is sports.

339
00:16:48,580 --> 00:16:49,820
Augar plays basketball,

340
00:16:49,860 --> 00:16:54,020
but I'm not very good at it,
so I have to improve my basketball skills.

341
00:16:54,860 --> 00:16:56,140
Go for it. You can do it.

342
00:16:56,180 --> 00:16:57,020
You've got this.

343
00:16:58,740 --> 00:17:01,500
That last line. It's seriously handsome.

344
00:17:01,580 --> 00:17:01,940
[PAUL TANAN as ACHI]

345
00:17:01,940 --> 00:17:02,940
He's kind of bold,
[PAUL TANAN as ACHI]

346
00:17:02,940 --> 00:17:03,100
[PAUL TANAN as ACHI]

347
00:17:03,100 --> 00:17:05,300
with a bit of a tough, gangster vibe.
[PAUL TANAN as ACHI]

348
00:17:05,300 --> 00:17:05,360
with a bit of a tough, gangster vibe.

349
00:17:05,940 --> 00:17:08,700
He's athletic, good-looking, and cool.

