wow, he jokes around a lot.

389
00:19:08,160 --> 00:19:10,460
His words are really funny.

390
00:19:10,480 --> 00:19:12,060
He can be a gagman.

391
00:19:12,160 --> 00:19:16,680
Though he has this funny side,
when he's quiet, he's really quiet.

392
00:19:16,860 --> 00:19:18,300
What is Ken like on set?

393
00:19:19,180 --> 00:19:20,300
He's very dedicated.

394
00:19:20,340 --> 00:19:22,920
He doesn't need much talking.

395
00:19:23,240 --> 00:19:25,920
Once he gets the script, he just reads it.

396
00:19:26,380 --> 00:19:28,180
No need to follow up or anything.

397
00:19:28,220 --> 00:19:31,020
Ken is someone
I find really easy to work with.

398
00:19:31,060 --> 00:19:32,180
Actually, we talk a lot.

399
00:19:32,220 --> 00:19:35,880
Ken is someone I hang out with
all the time.

400
00:19:35,900 --> 00:19:38,720
Ken and I are not that different.

401
00:19:39,420 --> 00:19:40,380
We get along really well.

402
