We learned acting together
when we first joined the company.

409
00:19:58,640 --> 00:20:02,060
We were paired up,
so we got to meet often.

410
00:20:02,100 --> 00:20:03,160
We were already close,

411
00:20:03,220 --> 00:20:04,900
