472
00:23:04,140 --> 00:23:08,220
He's very dedicated to his work
and studies the script a lot.

473
00:23:08,380 --> 00:23:11,580
I think he's really serious and committed.

474
00:23:11,960 --> 00:23:15,400
It feels good because
I've already become close to Paul.

475
00:23:15,420 --> 00:23:19,360
We get along well
